{"word":"G5399 - φοβέω - phobéō - fob-eh'-o - Be afraid","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φοβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>phobéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>fob-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be afraid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயப்படு, பயந்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to be put to flight, to flee"},{"paragraph":"2. to fear, be afraid"},{"paragraph":"3. to reverence, venerate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; to <i>frighten</i>, that is, (passively) to <i>be alarmed</i>; by analogy to <i>be in awe</i> of, that is, <i>revere:</i> - be (+ sore) afraid, fear (exceedingly), reverence."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5399 - φοβέω - phobéō - fob-eh'-o/5399\">G5399</a>, <a href=\"#/G5400 - φόβητρον - phóbētron - fob'-ay-tron/5400\">G5400</a>, <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>"}]}